        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>YE</strong> (5 pts) — archaic "you," valid in all tournament dictionaries</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>AY, OY</strong> — Y as the second letter, equally important for crossword plays</span></li>
      </ul>

